Forget Top Billing. If you wanted to witness a magical wedding, all you needed to do was watch social media at the weekend. That's when Mzansi celebrated Somizi and Mohale's traditional ceremony. The pair tied the knot at Mohale's family home in Kibler Park, Johannesburg, on September 28 2019. It was a star-studded affair, with some of Mzansi's most famous faces in attendance.